<item>
            <title>[SOLR-9885] Allow pre-startup Solr log management in Solr bin scripts to be disabled.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9885</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is log rotation and log archiver in solr starter script, which is failing if solr is deployed with custom log configuration (different log filename). Also inconvenient if using custom log rotation/management.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/lucene-solr/blob/master/solr/bin/solr#L1464&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/lucene-solr/blob/master/solr/bin/solr#L1464&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Proposing an environment setting, something like &lt;tt&gt;SOLR_LOG_PRESTART_ROTATION&lt;/tt&gt; (with default &lt;tt&gt;true&lt;/tt&gt;), that makes the execution of the four lines configurable.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
